narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Gotta take it. Start assignments early - work on the drawing just as much. Make sketch models!
You gotta do what you gotta do. It's all good grad school prep.

Certainly more manageable than 250. The work slows down a bit, though only relatively speaking. Arch 251 is a lesson in prioritization as much as anything else: its a given that you will not be able to accomplish as much as you want to - you are forced to make smart, selective decisions.
